
                      A Dual Games Port A-D Converter.
                      --------------------------------


    Minimum Requirements:-
    ----------------------

    1) A 1MB AMIGA A500.
    2) Workbench 1.3x.
    3) OCS.
    4) A PAL/NTSC television set.
    5) A floppy disk drive.
    6) The mouse.
    7) The software has NOT been tested on Workbench 1.2x or less.
    8) The software has NOT been tested on Workbench 3.1x or greater.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

    General Information:-
    ---------------------

    This tool is a dual Analogue to Digital Converter using the Games Port.
    It is linear to + or - 5% or better inside its working parameters,
    which is good enough for some of the future projects to be built.

